OL,5,G1900 Ben Fogle: New Lives in the Wild
OL,6,     FBen Fogle revisits people living
OL,7,     Foff-grid to see how their lives
OL,8,     Fhave progressed. Ben heads back to
OL,9,     Fthe swamplands of Georgia, to
OL,10,     Fcatch up with wild-man Colbert.
OL,11,G2000 Ben Fogle: New Lives in the Wild
OL,12,     FAustralia - Ben returns to the
OL,13,     Fwest coast of Australia to revisit
OL,14,     FJim and Kim, who both suffered
OL,15,     Fseparate life-threatening injuries
OL,16,     Fbefore finding solace in the wild
OL,17,     Fwith each other.
